sub_a_adv02.name: Hey, It's Me!
sub_a_adv02.explanation:
The scammers never stop figuring out
new ways to part an idiot from his money.

sub_a_adv03.name: Haruka's Biggest Fan
sub_a_adv03.explanation:
Ayaka was happy about the Haruka
merchandise I gave her. I definitely
need to show Haruka that picture.

sub_a_adv04.name: Runaway Robot
sub_a_adv04.explanation:
I didn't think I'd ever have to chase down
a cleaning robot. It's kinda romantic that
the little thing brought those two
together, though.

sub_a_adv05.name: I, Hiji
sub_a_adv05.explanation:
The digital personal assistant, "Hiji"...
She was convenient, but I don't like a
machine making me do things without my
consent.

sub_a_adv06.name: Like, Comment, Subscribe
sub_a_adv06.explanation:
It's fine to take a risk by posting videos
online, but it's not okay to cause trouble
for other people. Well, I'm sure he
learned his lesson.

sub_a_adv07.name: Follow That Drone!
sub_a_adv07.explanation:
Using a drone to gather information...
Technology is moving too fast.

sub_a_adv08.name: Baring Their Fangs
sub_a_adv08.explanation:
To think someone from the Snake Flower
Triad was still in this city... It's
probably best for me to lay low with
how Kamurocho currently is.

sub_a_adv09.name: A Rivalry Reborn
sub_a_adv09.explanation:
The remnants of the Snake Flower Triad had
such an elaborate plan. But now with this, that
group should be quiet for a while.

sub_a_adv11.name: Swipe Right
sub_a_adv11.explanation:
Someone was running a blackmail scheme
through Troublr. Some things really are
too good to be true...

sub_a_adv12.name: A Favor for an Old Friend
sub_a_adv12.explanation:
Date-san's account was hijacked...
There are so many ways to commit fraud,
I need to stay aware of them.

sub_b_adv01.name: The Fools Who Dream
sub_b_adv01.explanation:
I'm sure there will be lots of trials
ahead of you, but you'll become a great
idol in Tokyo, Misa.

sub_a_adv13.name: The Legendary Paul Lim
sub_a_adv13.explanation:
I met the legendary darts player,
Paul Lim. It might not hurt to polish
my darts skills when I get a chance.

sub_a_adv14.name: Showdown with Paul Lim
sub_a_adv14.explanation:
I took on Paul Lim in a darts match and he
was indeed amazing. I'll ask him for
another match sometime.

sub_a_adv15.name: Face Your Fears
sub_a_adv15.explanation:
Saki is a great professional wrestler and
gives courage to her fans. I'm cheering
you on too. Keep doing your best.

sub_a_adv16.name: A Shady Business
sub_a_adv16.explanation:
While there was a lot of fuss, it helped
me get to know Hikaru a little better.
I'm still going to support and protect
her however I can.

sub_a_adv17.name: Listen to Your Heart
sub_a_adv17.explanation:
I was able to have a nice long talk with
Sora so we could get to know each other
better. She taught me the importance of
thinking about my family.

sub_a_adv18.name: Caught in a Love Triangle
sub_a_adv18.explanation:
Erina won't have to worry about that
stalker anymore. Always stay true to
who you are, Erina.

sub_a_adv19.name: The Hostess with a Heart of Gold
sub_a_adv19.explanation:
Everyone loves Riona because of the
standards she holds herself to as a
hostess. She's really quite something.

sub_a_adv20.name: Step Up to the Plate
sub_a_adv20.explanation:
I became friends with Manager Yoshida from
the Batting Center and he joined my
baseball team. His knowledge of the game
might prove to be pretty useful!

sub_a_adv21.name: A Promise Between Men
sub_a_adv21.explanation:
Gori-san promised to join our team in
Hiroshima after I won his Home Run
contest. I'm excited to see how he plays.

sub_a_adv23.name: Look What the Dragon Dragged In
sub_a_adv23.explanation:
Finding cats for the cat café, eh? I guess
I'm doing it. I'll contact the owner
whenever a cat becomes friendly with me.

sub_a_adv24.name: The Temptation of Live Chat
sub_a_adv24.explanation:
Something called a "Live Chat" is popular
nowadays. Well, it's important to know the
trends. I should visit an internet café to
check it out when I have some free time.

sub_a_adv25.name: We're Committed to Results
sub_a_adv25.explanation:
Committed to results, huh? If I train
here, I'm sure my body will stay fit.
I'll make use of this place regularly.

sub_a_adv26.name: A Man Rises Up
sub_a_adv26.explanation:
Sodachi is committed to results as well.
He said he wants to fight me again...

sub_b_adv15.name: The Throne of Onomichi
sub_b_adv15.explanation:
We beat the Onomichi Legends! Next up is
the best team in the league, the Kanamizawa
Gorgeous. We have to win to protect our
precious field!

sub_b_adv02.name: Sins of the Father
sub_b_adv02.explanation:
Old man Suzuki may have founded a bogus
cult, but anyone who decides to atone for
his sins properly is a good person in my
book.

sub_b_adv03.name: Pocket Circuit Fighter Returns
sub_b_adv03.explanation:
Pocket Circuit Fighter has a nice life as
a tofu store owner and a father. I hope I
can have a Pocket Circuit match with him
again one day.

sub_b_adv04.name: The Curse of Onomichi
sub_b_adv04.explanation:
An odd, old man... Pirate ghosts... Was it
all just some weird hallucination? I feel
a little uneasy after all of that.

sub_b_adv05.name: Oh No! It's Ono Michio!
sub_b_adv05.explanation:
Well, it might not be bad to experience
wearing a mascot costume once in my life.
Although I get the feeling that this
isn't the last of Ono Michio-kun.

sub_b_adv06.name: The Ono Michio Show
sub_b_adv06.explanation:
To think I'd have to become Ono Michio
again for a concert... Ono Michio is
becoming a beloved mascot!

sub_b_adv07.name: Putting on a Brave Face
sub_b_adv07.explanation:
I became Ono Michio to give a girl the
courage to go through surgery. Mascots
have the power to give more than just
smiles; they can give strength.

sub_b_adv08.name: The Girl Who Leapt Through Time?
sub_b_adv08.explanation:
That girl claims she's from the future...
Heh, if we meet again, I should have her
bet on a horse race for me.

sub_b_adv09.name: A Freaky Situation
sub_b_adv09.explanation:
It seems Kazuo and Kazumi are going to
keep up the body swap act... But I'm
sure it'll work out. I hope they find
happiness.

sub_b_adv11.name: Assemble the Team
sub_b_adv11.explanation:
I've become the captain of the
Setouchi Warriors thanks to Chiba.
I have no idea how this is going
to turn out...

sub_b_adv12.name: We Need a Ringer
sub_b_adv12.explanation:
We recruited Moritsuka and we'll be going
against the Jingai Thunders' second team.
We'll still need some more players for
the match.

sub_b_adv13.name: The Sweet Taste of Victory
sub_b_adv13.explanation:
The Setouchi Warriors were able to seize
their first victory. We can't lose our
next match against the Thunders' primary
team!

sub_b_adv14.name: Decisive Battle! Jingai Thunders
sub_b_adv14.explanation:
We beat the Jingai Thunders, but then we
were challenged to a game against the
Onomichi Legends. They're supposed to be
an amazing team, but we're getting better
each day. Let's give them everything we've
got!

sub_b_adv16.name: True Bonds
sub_b_adv16.explanation:
We won against the Kanamizawa Gorgeous
and protected our home turf.
Setouchi Warriors... You've really
become an incredible team.

sub_b_adv17.name: What's the Matter with Kids Today?
sub_b_adv17.explanation:
Hatakeyama-san, make sure to value the
time you spend with your daughter.

sub_b_adv18.name: Powerful Memories
sub_b_adv18.explanation:
We convinced Akiyoshi-san to go to his
reunion. But I wonder what kind of
person his teacher is...

sub_b_adv19.name: Tech Support
sub_b_adv19.explanation:
Gen-san went from being afraid of high
tech items to being obsessed with them.
I'm just glad he's back to doing karaoke.

sub_b_adv20.name: The Price of Love
sub_b_adv20.explanation:
I'm glad Ando-san was able to get back
with his wife. I wasn't sure how things
would end, but everything worked out.

sub_b_adv21.name: Kaneko's Resolve
sub_b_adv21.explanation:
I'm glad Kaneko-san could come to terms
with his past and take a new step forward.

sub_b_adv22.name: Thanks for Everything, Mama
sub_b_adv22.explanation:
I told Mama how grateful I was for all
she's done. Having a drink is great, but
even greater when you have it with
friends.

sub_b_adv23.name: The Old Man and the Sea
sub_b_adv23.explanation:
I never imagined I'd go spearfishing at
some point in my life... But there's a
surprising amount of depth to it. I'll
go out to sea again when I have time.

sub_b_adv24.name: World's Best Octopus
sub_b_adv24.explanation:
I caught a Delicious Octopus because
Kenji Gorchov, the baseball player, begged
for it. I wonder what else I can catch out
here with such a unique flavor.

sub_b_adv25.name: Deep Blue Sea
sub_b_adv25.explanation:
I managed to defeat the Bloody Shark and
everyone is able to fish again. I should
come back to this special place to fish
again sometime.

sub_b_adv26.name: Crisis Management Professional
sub_b_adv26.explanation:
I'm going to be battling with Saigo, a
crisis management professional, from now
on. He's an odd man, but I'll learn what I
can from him.

sub_b_adv27.name: The Joys of Adulthood
sub_b_adv27.explanation:
A bar... It might be nice to have a drink
and enjoy some small talk. I'd like to sit
back and relax every now and then.
